  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/963280/extras/17dc93ca714cbbb2a9dd1246f3fbbdf8.poster.avif?t=1772898107\" width=616 height=210 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/963280/extras/17dc93ca714cbbb2a9dd1246f3fbbdf8.webm?t=1772898107\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/963280/extras/17dc93ca714cbbb2a9dd1246f3fbbdf8.mp4?t=1772898107\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>Work for Sunny Morning™</strong> and sell products of the most varied natures!<br><strong>What kinds of products</strong>, you ask? Do not worry about it, your role is only to sell them. :)<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/963280/extras/86c478fb9300d7f24119840a43b5d1ed.poster.avif?t=1772898107\" width=616 height=210 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/963280/extras/86c478fb9300d7f24119840a43b5d1ed.webm?t=1772898107\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/963280/extras/86c478fb9300d7f24119840a43b5d1ed.mp4?t=1772898107\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>Each step</strong> of the conversation can <strong>increase or decrease</strong> your Rage, Depression and <strong>SALES! :O</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/963280/extras/a8a933c28d3149961eaf83c39aae6571.poster.avif?t=1772898107\" width=616 height=210 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/963280/extras/a8a933c28d3149961eaf83c39aae6571.webm?t=1772898107\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/963280/extras/a8a933c28d3149961eaf83c39aae6571.mp4?t=1772898107\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>Choose carefully</strong> which house to visit at each time of the day: The <strong>mood</strong> of each potential buyer <strong>varies</strong> with time!<br><strong>Balance your spending</strong> between Motel daily costs and items that help you deal with Rage and Depression.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/963280/extras/196978f85dff302d060f8cdb528286db.poster.avif?t=1772898107\" width=616 height=210 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/963280/extras/196978f85dff302d060f8cdb528286db.webm?t=1772898107\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br>There are <strong>36 DIFFERENT ENDINGS</strong> in the game!!!",
